3x^2 - y^2 = 8
(4/3,0)
x-x_1=m(y-y_1) 
x-x_1=\frac{a}b{} (y-y_1)
bx-bx_1=ay-ay_1
y=\frac{bx-bx_1+ay_1}{a}
y=mx
